Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.78,0:01:35.94,Default,,0,0,0,,- I'm gonna go look.\N- You're not!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.03,0:01:38.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna go look for {\i1}my{\i0} woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.88,0:01:40.79,Default,,0,0,0,,You can go look for the other one.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.62,0:01:47.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you seeing Julia behind my back?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.73,0:01:52.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I feel like I'm in a confession booth.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.59,0:01:55.00,Default,,0,0,0,,You're not a preacher\Nby any chance, are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.09,0:01:58.09,Default,,0,0,0,,If there's anyone who\Nneeds pity here, it's you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.01,0:02:02.93,Default,,0,0,0,,We still haven't settled\Nthe score from last time.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.33,0:02:06.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Make your move.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.23,0:02:12.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Step aside, Lin!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.19,0:02:16.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Lin...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.66,0:02:47.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I was in the same squadron\Nas Vicious on Titan.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.11,0:02:52.54,Default,,0,0,0,,You said that you didn't need comrades.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.63,0:02:54.82,Default,,0,0,0,,But I'm attracted to that word.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.13,0:02:58.19,Default,,0,0,0,,To the point of tears.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.28,0:03:03.24,Default,,0,0,0,,You see, that's what we were\Nat Titan. We were all comrades.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.48,0:03:55.29,Default,,0,0,0,,What's that song?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.54,0:04:00.04,Default,,0,0,0,,"Julia."
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.13,0:04:02.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Nice melody.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.33,0:04:08.77,Default,,0,0,0,,You mind if I play that tune on\Nmy sax when I get back home?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.21,0:04:55.39,Default,,0,0,0,,When I came home from the war,\Nthey put me in prison.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.48,0:04:58.14,Default,,0,0,0,,They thought I was a spy.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.23,0:05:01.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I heard it was Vicious\Nthat testified against me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.19,0:05:03.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I started to go crazy.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.70,0:05:07.32,Default,,0,0,0,,So they gave me some new drug\Nthey were testing on prisoners.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.41,0:05:10.80,Default,,0,0,0,,It was highly addictive.\NAnd the side effects, well...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.89,0:05:14.74,Default,,0,0,0,,My hormones went out of balance,\Nand this is what happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.83,0:05:18.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Since I came here, there's been one\Nother person who knew about Vicious.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.66,0:05:20.37,Default,,0,0,0,,You're only the second one.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.46,0:05:22.80,Default,,0,0,0,,And the second one I've told about this.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.57,0:05:25.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you going to see Vicious?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.02,0:05:28.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Didn't you say he framed you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.41,0:05:32.76,Default,,0,0,0,,- I want to find out if he did.\N- He'll murder you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.85,0:05:35.85,Default,,0,0,0,,- Death does not frighten me.\N- You're lying.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.04,0:05:39.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Either way, I don't have long to live.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.67,0:05:43.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Why did you bring me here?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.07,0:05:49.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe I wanted to be\Nwith someone, I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.53,0:05:53.41,Default,,0,0,0,,You just help someone selfishly,\Nand you take them home...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.50,0:05:55.62,Default,,0,0,0,,And then you go off to die.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.81,0:06:10.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you sure it was this woman?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.01,0:06:12.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.58,0:06:15.59,Default,,0,0,0,,It's been six months since\NI saw a woman in the flesh.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.68,0:06:18.09,Default,,0,0,0,,And two years since I saw\Na girl that good-looking.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.18,0:06:20.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Trust me, I wouldn't make\Na mistake about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.36,0:06:23.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Man, I sure wouldn't\Nwanna live around here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.76,0:06:26.46,Default,,0,0,0,,She sat over there, talking to Gren.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.55,0:06:30.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Julia used to sit in that same seat.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.20,0:06:31.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Julia?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.87,0:06:34.73,Default,,0,0,0,,About two years ago,\Nshe wandered in outta the blue.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.82,0:06:36.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Month later, she disappeared.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.66,0:06:38.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah? What kinda girl was she?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.10,0:06:42.34,Default,,0,0,0,,She was a real woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.89,0:06:49.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm the only one who can keep you alive.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.86,0:06:53.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And I'm the only one who can kill you.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.06,0:06:57.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm just watching a dream\Nthat I never wake up from.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.31,0:06:59.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's like I'm watching a dream.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.50,0:07:03.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Be careful when you're with that woman.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.46,0:07:06.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Women are all liars.\NYou should know that.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.69,0:07:11.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}When this is over,\NI'm getting out of it. All of it.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.56,0:07:14.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}When I do, will you come with me?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.54,0:07:19.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Are you going to betray me?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.93,0:07:24.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}No, please... They're gonna kill you!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.50,0:07:26.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Oh, you're finally up.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.24,0:07:28.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You've been sleeping for three days.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.34,0:07:34.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Your eyes are different colors.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.28,0:07:36.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}My left eye sees the past.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.68,0:07:40.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And? What about your right eye?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.22,0:07:57.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not dead. How about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.18,0:08:14.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Which way is west?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.29,0:08:19.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks a bunch, pal.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.10,0:08:27.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Tranquilizer guns. They're mocking me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.82,0:08:57.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me, I'm looking for a blue building.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.62,0:09:00.25,Default,,0,0,0,,It's called the Orlando Apartments.\NDo you know where it is?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.34,0:09:03.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh... I don't know nothing.\NAsk somebody else.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.33,0:09:04.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.90,0:09:08.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Forget it. I don't want anything\Nto do with foreigners ever again.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.63,0:09:10.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm just asking for directions.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.36,0:09:13.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna go find an\Nhonest job somewhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.83,0:09:20.97,Default,,0,0,0,,What's up with him?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.44,0:09:31.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Blue apartment building...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.12,0:10:00.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Hey, wake up!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.91,0:10:05.41,Default,,0,0,0,,It's you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.50,0:10:07.94,Default,,0,0,0,,What the hell is this all about?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.44,0:10:11.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.30,0:10:13.58,Default,,0,0,0,,He's one of {\i1}those{\i0} kinda guys, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.67,0:10:15.73,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.82,0:10:18.80,Default,,0,0,0,,You mean Gren?\NHe's not like anyone else.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.89,0:10:20.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Gren again.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.81,0:10:28.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Mangan with double reverse dragon...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.04,0:10:31.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Great... he's using an ancient code.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.78,0:10:38.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Julia was here. Right in this town.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.81,0:10:45.07,Default,,0,0,0,,- {\i1}Yo.{\i0}\N- What.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.16,0:10:47.66,Default,,0,0,0,,- {\i1}Got anything?{\i0}\N- No.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.75,0:10:50.54,Default,,0,0,0,,- {\i1}I got a lead.{\i0}\N- Catch him yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.63,0:10:54.23,Default,,0,0,0,,This guy's from the group\Nyou're after. Code name Julia.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.32,0:10:57.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}His name's Gren.\NEscaped from a military prison.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.42,0:10:59.94,Default,,0,0,0,,He has a very hefty bounty on his head.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.03,0:11:03.63,Default,,0,0,0,,If you catch him, I'll...\Nlet you back on.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.31,0:11:15.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.73,0:11:18.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm standing above you.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.23,0:11:21.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Come to the roof of the building\Nthat's closest to the sky.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.32,0:11:24.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll send a woman over.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.33,0:11:25.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Up to you.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.07,0:11:30.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Although, I was looking forward\Nto seeing you... personally.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.32,0:11:35.50,Default,,0,0,0,,You messed up the Bebop,\Nbut left the other ships intact.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.59,0:11:37.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Swordfish and Hammerhead\Nare fully mobile.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.03,0:11:41.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Was that like a hint for us\Nto come and find you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.59,0:11:44.21,Default,,0,0,0,,You're joking, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.30,0:11:47.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Were you just testing us or what?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.10,0:11:48.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Why'd you come after me?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.06,0:11:51.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I want my money back.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.24,0:11:53.06,Default,,0,0,0,,- The ship's safe...\N- Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.15,0:11:55.79,Default,,0,0,0,,It only had 20,000 in it, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.88,0:11:57.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.43,0:11:58.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Dummy.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.21,0:12:03.12,Default,,0,0,0,,So who is this Julia?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.21,0:12:04.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.87,0:12:07.28,Default,,0,0,0,,She's got some kinda hold on Spike.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.37,0:12:09.39,Default,,0,0,0,,That's all I can tell you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.71,0:12:38.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Where's my souvenir?\NIs it here? Is it here yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.15,0:13:24.27,Default,,0,0,0,,It's reading X-plus. It's real.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.36,0:13:25.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Give it to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.89,0:13:30.49,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the Titan opal you requested.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.37,0:13:34.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Tell Gren that I send my regards.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.87,0:13:38.54,Default,,0,0,0,,You saved me from\Nthat scorpion, and yet...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.63,0:13:41.59,Default,,0,0,0,,you lied and sold me down the river.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.86,0:14:02.86,Default,,0,0,0,,It's you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.63,0:14:05.23,Default,,0,0,0,,It's been a long time.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.32,0:14:07.32,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you want?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.41,0:14:09.39,Default,,0,0,0,,When you gave me that music box,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.48,0:14:12.30,Default,,0,0,0,,you didn't think I'd ever\Nbreak it open and look inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.39,0:14:13.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Why would I?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.83,0:14:16.48,Default,,0,0,0,,So you found the solar transmitter.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.57,0:14:18.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Julia found it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.25,0:14:20.62,Default,,0,0,0,,The moment she heard\Nit was a gift from you,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.71,0:14:22.58,Default,,0,0,0,,she told me to open it up and look.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.67,0:14:25.35,Default,,0,0,0,,And? What about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.44,0:14:28.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you trying to kill me again?\NIs that it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.66,0:14:32.19,Default,,0,0,0,,We fought that bloody war together.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.28,0:14:34.14,Default,,0,0,0,,We were comrades.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.68,0:14:42.36,Default,,0,0,0,,We risked everything, shoulder to shoulder,\Non that battleground of death.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.36,0:14:45.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I looked up to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.57,0:14:50.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I believed in you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.83,0:14:55.79,Default,,0,0,0,,There was nothing to believe in.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.54,0:15:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no need to believe.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.42,0:15:03.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Vicious, look out!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.54,0:15:25.27,Default,,0,0,0,,There is nothing in\Nthis world to believe in.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.74,0:15:34.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Vicious!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.70,0:15:38.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Lin died protecting you!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.00,0:15:41.41,Default,,0,0,0,,His soul is lost!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.50,0:15:43.95,Default,,0,0,0,,He wasn't protecting me!\NDon't you get it?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.04,0:15:46.13,Default,,0,0,0,,He was protecting the Order!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.77,0:16:08.34,Default,,0,0,0,,You're in the way!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.31,0:17:47.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, come on! Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.29,0:17:50.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Gren, tell me where Julia is!\NI've gotta find her!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.19,0:17:55.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Julia's gone. How did you know her?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.26,0:17:57.64,Default,,0,0,0,,What happened? I need to know.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.97,0:18:07.22,Default,,0,0,0,,You've got an internal injury.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.31,0:18:10.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know if an ambulance\Nwill even come out to this place.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.42,0:18:15.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Put it away.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.99,0:18:18.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you lift me up there\Nonto the ship again?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.93,0:18:22.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to go to Titan.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.32,0:18:26.49,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't make it there in this\Ncondition, it would take too long.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.58,0:18:28.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not gonna make it anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.91,0:18:32.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Dying on my way there\Nwould be a good way to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.59,0:18:35.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I wanna go back one last time.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.88,0:18:37.67,Default,,0,0,0,,If I can't do that...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.38,0:18:41.32,Default,,0,0,0,,then at least help me on my way.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.41,0:18:43.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you help me take off?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.03,0:18:58.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I get it now.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.12,0:19:00.49,Default,,0,0,0,,You're the one, aren't you?\NYou're Spike.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.49,0:19:04.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Julia was always talking about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.49,0:19:08.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Your eyes are different colors.\NI remember her saying that.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.92,0:19:12.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Said you'd get a strange feeling,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.50,0:19:15.33,Default,,0,0,0,,if you'd keep looking\Nstraight into his eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.42,0:19:17.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Where'd you meet her?\NWhere was she?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.07,0:19:20.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Right on the corner bar stool.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.21,0:19:22.09,Default,,0,0,0,,She'd slip in when I wasn't looking.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.18,0:19:26.26,Default,,0,0,0,,She'd ask me to play the same\Nsong every time she came in.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.35,0:19:29.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Strange, lilting tune.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.31,0:19:31.99,Default,,0,0,0,,And then she would smile.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.08,0:19:34.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, what a smile.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.16,0:19:36.98,Default,,0,0,0,,So sad.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.15,0:19:40.45,Default,,0,0,0,,So beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.78,0:20:50.89,Default,,0,0,0,,- What are you bringing in?\N- {\i1}Nothing.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.37,0:20:55.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Hurry up and get inside.\NWe're taking off.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.68,0:21:08.13,Default,,0,0,0,,- Julia...\N- What'd you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.22,0:21:12.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm? Oh, nothing.\NJust thinking about someone.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.35,0:21:14.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Where'd you guys go, anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.36,0:21:15.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Someplace very good.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.04,0:21:18.64,Default,,0,0,0,,How come Edward got left out?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.73,0:21:21.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh... I'll tell you about it someday.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.87,0:21:23.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Nah, it's all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.76,0:21:26.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Ed... anything but blue.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.61,0:21:45.25,Default,,0,0,0,,A star just fell from the sky.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.34,0:21:48.30,Default,,0,0,0,,That is not an ordinary star, my son.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.39,0:21:50.64,Default,,0,0,0,,That star is the tear of a warrior.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.73,0:21:52.53,Default,,0,0,0,,What warrior is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.62,0:21:56.83,Default,,0,0,0,,A lost soul who has finished his\Nbattle somewhere on this planet.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.46,0:22:02.25,Default,,0,0,0,,A pitiful soul who could not\Nfind his way to the lofty realm
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.34,0:22:05.57,Default,,0,0,0,,where the Great Spirit awaits us all.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.36,0:24:13.76,Default,,0,0,0,,What is going on in this world?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.85,0:24:17.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Though you're alive,\Ndarkness looms only inches away.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.68,0:24:21.33,Default,,0,0,0,,A world where any move you make\Ncould be a dangerous mistake.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.42,0:24:23.83,Default,,0,0,0,,So we will step away\Nfrom the mainstream
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.92,0:24:27.06,Default,,0,0,0,,and live like vagabonds\Nand common dropouts.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.15,0:24:30.62,Default,,0,0,0,,A psychedelic rhapsody\Nfor someone just like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.71,0:24:35.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Next episode:\N"Bohemian Rhapsody."
Dialogue: 0,0:24:35.13,0:24:38.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you wanna hang out\Nand waste your life with us?
